org.cs2c.nginlib
类 MiddlewareFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.cs2c.nginlib.MiddlewareFactory

public abstract class MiddlewareFactory
extends java.lang.Object

作者：
Mikes

The MiddlewareFactory is the entry of the library. Each instance of this class is associated with a specific remote middleware (not remote host). Through the instance of the class, we can further get to configure, control and monitor the remote middleware.

方法详细信息

getInstance

public static MiddlewareFactory getInstance(AuthInfo authInfo,
                                            java.lang.String middlewareHome)
                                     throws RemoteException
Get an instance of the class based on remote middleware home path.

参数：
authInfo - Remote host access information
返回：
the instance binded with the specific remote middleware.
抛出：
RemoteException - When authentication fails, network error or nginx does not exist.

install

public static MiddlewareFactory install(AuthInfo authInfo,
                                        java.io.File gzFile,
                                        java.lang.String targetPath,
                                        java.util.List<Module> modules)
                                 throws java.io.IOException,
                                        RemoteException
If remote middleware is not there, we can call this method to install it remotely. Before installing, a local setup file should be prepared.

参数：
authInfo - Authentication info in order to access remote host.
gzFile - middleware setup file in local. Format must be tar.gz.
targetPath - The path in remote host where the middleware will be installed.
modules - Which modules should be included when middleware (such as Nginx) is installed.
返回：
the instance of the class, which is binded with the middleware installed.
抛出：
java.io.IOException - When reading local gzFile fails.
RemoteException - When installing remote nginx fails.

getController

public abstract Controller getController()
Get the controller interface in order to operate Nginx' running. The Nginx is binded with the instance.

返回：
The Controller interface of the middleware (Nginx).

getConfigurator

public abstract Configurator getConfigurator()
Get the configurator interface in order to operate Nginx configure file. The Nginx is binded with the instance.

返回：
The configurator interface of the middleware (Nginx).

getMonitor

public abstract Monitor getMonitor()
Get the monitor interface in order to fetch the remote host and middleware's running status. The Nginx is binded with the instance.

返回：
The monitor interface of the middleware (Nginx).

newAuthInfo

public abstract AuthInfo newAuthInfo()
Create an instance of AuthInfo without any info. Then you can set the instance info through AuthInfo interface.

返回：
An instance of AuthInfo without any info.
